{"tid":995079,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"Twitch: 2019年2月4日至8日, 邵氏功夫電影馬拉松","createTime":"2019-01-25T07:34:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-05T08:44:01.000Z","uid":36509,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f31c555c3a6a9036bf0e3b6f0f0da1407ab290fd","tid":995079,"uid":36509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T07:34:39.000Z","msg":"天映娛樂和GammaRay今天宣佈，將於2019年2月4日至8日期間，Twitch（<a href=\"http://twitch.tv/gammaray_tv\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwitch.tv%2Fgammaray_tv&d=1JqvwWNHjQPDp8tWt%2FwICh4KspRE1ZdqvS7v6cf6aI4%3D&h=a70b2687\" target=\"_blank\">http://twitch.tv/gammaray_tv</a>）以馬拉松方式串流播放邵氏電影，慶祝農曆新年。<br />\n<br />\n邵氏功夫電影馬拉松是 GammaRay 首次在 Twitch 足本播放電影。在2月4日至8日的馬拉松式播出後，逢星期四和星期五自下午5:00時（太平洋時間）起再每晚播放兩套電影，為期四周。<br />\n<br />\nTwitch 串流直播期間將會播放<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>44套</strong></span>電影，包括以下的經典功夫電影：<br />\n<br />\n《天下第一拳》（1972年）：一名功夫弟子（羅烈飾）前往參加全國國術大賽，途中屢遇挑戰，荊棘滿途。<br />\n《殘缺》（1978年）：天道莊莊主杜天道（陳觀泰飾）自妻子去世後性情大變，在兇殘暴戾的兒子助紂為虐下橫霸鄉里，害人無數。其中四個受害者分別被弄瞎、折斷腿、弄啞弄聾和傷害至神經失常，其後拜名師為徒，練就一身武藝後為民除害。<br />\n《五毒》（1978年）：五毒門掌門人在臨終前命關門弟子清理門戶，剷除為非作歹的五位師兄，但他們分別精通五毒門一門獨特武功，導致連番惡鬥。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.prnasia.com/story/235826-2.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.prnasia.com%2Fstory%2F235826-2.shtml&d=1JqvwWNHjQPDp8tWt%2FwICh4KspRE1ZdqvS7v6cf6aI4%3D&h=75b99cac\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.prnasia.com/story/235826-2.shtml</a>"},{"pid":"c1bbae769bdac935ffab64bcae549732abe88190","tid":995079,"uid":36087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T07:50:13.000Z","msg":"舊戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4821f16b8ff35194056c091abbb01fc2a2328a3d","tid":995079,"uid":36509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T12:16:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.twitch.tv/gammaray_tv\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.twitch.tv%2Fgammaray_tv&d=1JqvwWNHjQPDp8tWt%2FwI